{"type":"article","id":14287,"title":"中共通过修改“确诊病例”的定义隐瞒疫情！","uid":12147,"topics":[5889,5659,5262],"contents":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lwcalex/status/1226840055869632512\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lwcalex/status/1226840055869632512</a><br>\n<br>\n中共政府2月7日下发的一份工作指引文件中，要求医疗人员把无症状的感染者单独列为“阳性检测”一类进行上报，不再计入“确诊病例”，等无症状感染者出现临床症状后，再计入“确诊病例”，这么做会大大降低“确诊病例”的数字。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQachl_UYAAJQ1I?format=jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQachl_UYAAJQ1I?format=jpg\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EQachl_UYAAJQ1I?format=jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DrEricDing/status/1226868235192152065\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@哈佛丁教授</a>直指这种行为是officially cheating（官方作弊）！","date":"2020-02-10","agreeCount":16,"discussionCount":0}